                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d292">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 862.413St4/32.</note>
                <head>[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="italic">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-06-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 20, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reports that September 2 is proposed by the Emperor as the date for the
                    presentation of the statue of Gen. von Steuben; also that the appointment of C.
                    P. Wolfram as special representative of the President is agreeable to the German
                    Emperor.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hill.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
